text: Peptides from the SCX fractions were dissolved in 0 . 3 µl 100 % formic acid and diluted to 5 µl in 0 . 05 % trifluoroacetic acid ( TFA ) . The peptides were loaded onto a micrOTOF - Q II - nano LC system ( Bruker Daltonics , Inc . , Billerica , MA , USA ) and mass spectra were acquired in the 250 - 1 , 600 m / z range every second for 60 min .
